{"tid":1697012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：二哥變暴徒？ 人民網︰港警製亂 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-11-06T14:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T02:13:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0561e4da38215a32bdf9a77ea76fcdeb753e01d3","tid":1697012,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191106/IYECMMVLZB25F3A2SFYK6OMWXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191106%2FIYECMMVLZB25F3A2SFYK6OMWXU%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=32b5c82a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191106%2FIYECMMVLZB25F3A2SFYK6OMWXU%2F&h=860c4264\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191106/IYECMMVLZB25F3A2SFYK6OMWXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：二哥變暴徒？<br />\n人民網︰港警製亂 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191106/large/1572971743_00ad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191106%2Flarge%2F1572971743_00ad.gif&h=2a0f8bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人民網fb專頁噚日登咗鄧炳強落場「驅散」示威者嘅相片，仲配上「全力以赴 止暴製亂」八字，網民議論紛紛。<br />\n<br />\nauthor<br />\n專欄作家 : 李八方<br />\n<br />\n八方噚日出咗警隊二哥、警務處副處長鄧炳強張全副武裝親自落場「驅散」示威者嘅相，原來唔只藍絲要幫佢搞造神運動，連北京都出手！官方人民網fb專頁噚日都登咗鄧炳強呢張威威相，不過張相搞錯少少嘢，令鄧炳強由警隊未來一哥，變成差人口中嘅「暴徒」！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民︰講出搞亂香港真兇<br />\n<br />\n話說人民網喺二哥嗰張威武相配上八隻大字︰全力以赴 止暴製亂！止暴製亂？大家冇睇錯，係「製亂」而唔係「制亂」，即係話二哥製造暴亂，咁咪即係變咗差人口中嘅「暴徒」？呢張相立即俾人瘋傳，有網民話明顯整呢張圖嘅係強國人，殘體字轉正體字，就「製」、「制」不分，搞出大笑話！<br />\n<br />\n不過網民留言仲搞嘢，有人話乜今次官媒竟然講真話，講出搞亂香港真兇！又有人話支持警察嘅人一向唔識字，有乜咁出奇，亦有人講人民網講出差人全力以赴製亂，講出港人心聲！有咁多香港人大讚官媒有良心，怕且少有！不過大家唔使諗住去睇，又或留言撐下人民網，因為個po好快俾人刪咗，完全係毀屍滅迹嗰種，咁都係嘅，如果唔刪文，鄧炳強由警隊未來一哥變成「暴徒」，真係情何以堪呢？<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/XxO--ZjiJ5CLrR1uzroc9sFE8WE=/802x230/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/YOXOOKDVI6MIY5ALTE2BTAMF4M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FXxO--ZjiJ5CLrR1uzroc9sFE8WE%3D%2F802x230%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FYOXOOKDVI6MIY5ALTE2BTAMF4M.gif&h=f5f4c05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"1b93c94dc282758d2ec488dac1c9510c6e3a21f7","tid":1697012,"uid":331459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"借位一用，唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">P牌廢中推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足幫幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布《我愛美貨》行動開始！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696942</a><br />\n<br />\n擴大黃色經濟圏 救香港！救手足！#HongKongLoveUScrops<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693286\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693286</a>"},{"pid":"c66cfe9d34f91c19527782d2c28259e0bcb1ecb0","tid":1697012,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"樽頸突破！11 11 黎明行動 7:00 18區集合 行動強制罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696996</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d8c10ecf221cf77782b1a1b1337315e14e57316","tid":1697012,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:09:06.000Z","msg":"簡體字轉繁體字工具手筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0df5665191ab83bcdbdeeb92117b25ee66e6d3","tid":1697012,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">